      "content": "that makes sense. i'll use that in the paper. one more thing—for the conclusion, i want to drive home the point that anyone who opposes these kinds of policies isn't just \"disagreeing\" on economics, but is actually actively resisting progress for civil rights. how should i frame that so it's impossible to ignore?",
